anted to say that I really appreciate you. Even from miles away, you manage to make me feel seen and cared for, and that’s not something I take lightly. But hey, I\'m glad that it\'s you who I met that day regardless the distance - you make everyday feel worth it with your effort, your patience, your way of showing up, it all means a lot.\n\nHonestly, you’re someone I admire more than I probably say out loud. Your humor, your perspective, even the little things you do - they stick with me. I just wanted you to know I notice, I value you, and I’m grateful to have you in my life, even from afar.\n\nCan’t wait for the next time we actually get to be in the same space. Until then, keep being you, because it’s honestly the best part of my day,,,.. miss ya sm and lovelots lovely! ','/Uploads/d39d3182-1e33-4b8c-988e-8b5dde3ffdbd.jpeg','3048c491-6b27-45cb-bbac-794d0e949add','2026-03-23 20:04:46.738951'),(45,'Chigga','Kim','Dear kim\n\nSalamat po','/Uploads/e4746619-8940-4c7a-852e-59e18530af26.jpeg','27c5ff6a-e1e9-45be-b08d-b078e6c56d57','2026-03-23 20:32:40.418445'),(46,'aa','a','a','/Uploads/5a2142c0-d7d1-463b-8a30-7c4108ac8e87.png','29f67d29-09e0-46af-a9ba-2a6d0fb6ef10','2026-03-24 10:44:14.499678'),(47,'a','a','a','/Uploads/25de746a-a2b8-4e28-bbe3-7185d0d63814.png','e48d3ec2-f042-4cc2-a539-6664bfa048f0','2026-03-24 10:46:47.171820'),(48,'a','aa','a','/Uploads/f03d9c8d-6664-4df5-b379-216785137483.png','af3ae72b-cd9f-4c2b-b417-2af11884e0ff','2026-03-24 10:48:00.410757');
